    <!--  帮助说明  -->
    <string name="help_msg">
        Brief instructions below, see project homepage for more.\n\n
        **Introduction:** GPTAssistant, based on ChatGPT, lets you set question templates for quick querying via desktop icon or notification bar.\n\n
        **OpenAI settings:** Fill in the OpenAI API host and API_Key in settings. Both official or relay services are supported.\n\n
        **Activate via volume key:** For voice assistant, enable accessibility service and allow background running. After that,\n\n1. Long-press volume down to wake the app,\n2. speak to the mic while holding,\n3. After release, press again within 3 seconds to send the query.\n\n
        **Speech to text:** The default HMS voice service can be switched to Baidu / Google / Whisper service, see project homepage for instruction.\n\n
        **Network access:** Enabling networking allows fetching web content for GPT to enhance answer accuracy. Note: This can increase token usage significantly.\n\n
        **Note:** If there\'s vibration without pop-up after long-pressing volume, please permit background pop-ups in system settings.
    </string>
